<h1>Problem 2168 - 2024 RMMSL, N2, N</h1>
<h2 class='difficulty'>Difficulty: 7</h2>
<p>Let \(a_1\) be a positive integer and \(a_n = \sum_{i=1}^{n-1} \gcd(n, a_i)\) for any \(n\geq 2\). Prove that \(a_{n+1} \leq a_n\) for infinitely many \(n\).</p>
